    "actions": [
      {
        "startDie": 1,
        "endDie": 2,
        "name": "Crushing Slam (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Bone Golem raises one of its massive arms and slams it down onto a target, dealing D6 Bludgeoning damage on a hit. The target must succeed on an Athletics check or be knocked Prone.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 3,
        "endDie": 4,
        "name": "Necrotic Grasp (Magical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Bone Golem reaches out with its skeletal hand, attempting to drain the life force of a target. It deals D6 Necrotic damage on a hit, regaining Health equal to half the damage dealt.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 5,
        "endDie": 6,
        "name": "Rending Strike (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Bone Golem strikes at a target with its jagged bone edges, attempting to tear through armor and flesh. It makes a melee attack, dealing D6 Slashing damage on a hit. If the attack hits a Location protected by Armor, an immediate Armor Integrity check must be made due to the Bone Golem's rending attack.</p></div>"
      }
    ],
    "description": "<div><p>Towering above most other creatures, the Bone Golem is a nightmarish fusion of skeletal fragments, held together by dark magic and ancient runes etched into its calcified surface. Its empty eye sockets glow with an eerie, malevolent light, and its articulated body moves with an unnatural fluidity, wielding immense strength and resilience and shrugging off all but the most potent of attacks. It lumbers forward with a relentless purpose, leaving a trail of desolation in its wake, and its thunderous footsteps resonate through the halls of Ker Nethalas.</p></div>",
